title: Fei Protocol Discord Was Not 'Seized' Amid Class-Action Lawsuit, Says Lawyer
description: A message appearing on Fei Labs' Discord alerted investors who may have been hurt by its shaky launch event in April 2021 on how to file a notice for compensation as part of an ongoing class-action lawsuit against the platform.
